{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01694rHhH8cBYTRVHAYRYJT2","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t// Public surface for the peek mutations module (FR-14).\n2\t//\n3\t// Subsequent FR-14 iterations import `runPeekMutation` to wire the\n4\t// approved mutation actions (KOL rate, fraud-flag status, dogpile cancel,\n5\t// reward-config edit) into route handlers, and import the registry types\n6\t// to register new mutation definitions alongside the framework.\n7\t\n8\texport {\n9\t  PEEK_MUTATIONS,\n10\t  getPeekMutation,\n11\t  type PeekMutationActionId,\n12\t  type PeekMutationActorContext,\n13\t  type PeekMutationDefinition,\n14\t  type PeekMutationExecuteContext,\n15\t  type PeekMutationExecuteResult,\n16\t  type PeekMutationRegistry,\n17\t} from \"./registry\";\n18\texport {\n19\t  runPeekMutation,\n20\t  type PeekMutationAuditWriter,\n21\t  type PeekMutationFailure,\n22\t  type PeekMutationFailureReason,\n23\t  type PeekMutationRunInput,\n24\t  type PeekMutationRunResult,\n25\t  type PeekMutationSuccess,\n26\t} from \"./runner\";\n27\texport {\n28\t  KOL_RATE_BPS_MAX,\n29\t  KOL_RATE_BPS_MIN,\n30\t  kolRateUpdateInputSchema,\n31\t  kolRateUpdateMutation,\n32\t  type KolRateUpdateInput,\n33\t} from \"./kol-rate\";\n34\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac0c4bb5-fd14-4fda-adaf-f3ade788ced5","uuid":"28abe05b-f434-41ac-93bd-d064747b5dea","timestamp":"2026-04-26T15:32:10.543Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/peek/src/server/mutations/index.ts","content":"// Public surface for the peek mutations module (FR-14).\n//\n// Subsequent FR-14 iterations import `runPeekMutation` to wire the\n// approved mutation actions (KOL rate, fraud-flag status, dogpile cancel,\n// reward-config edit) into route handlers, and import the registry types\n// to register new mutation definitions alongside the framework.\n\nexport {\n  PEEK_MUTATIONS,\n  getPeekMutation,\n  type PeekMutationActionId,\n  type PeekMutationActorContext,\n  type PeekMutationDefinition,\n  type PeekMutationExecuteContext,\n  type PeekMutationExecuteResult,\n  type PeekMutationRegistry,\n} from \"./registry\";\nexport {\n  runPeekMutation,\n  type PeekMutationAuditWriter,\n  type PeekMutationFailure,\n  type PeekMutationFailureReason,\n  type PeekMutationRunInput,\n  type PeekMutationRunResult,\n  type PeekMutationSuccess,\n} from \"./runner\";\nexport {\n  KOL_RATE_BPS_MAX,\n  KOL_RATE_BPS_MIN,\n  kolRateUpdateInputSchema,\n  kolRateUpdateMutation,\n  type KolRateUpdateInput,\n} from \"./kol-rate\";\n","numLines":34,"startLine":1,"totalLines":34}}}
